
 Show / manipulate routing, devices, policy routing and tunnels

 ip [ OPTIONS ] OBJECT { COMMAND | help }

 ip addr add|del [address[/mask]] dev [nic] 	# not permanent
 ip addr show 
 ip link set [iface] up|down
 ip route show
 ip route get

 ip -o|oneline
 ip -s|--stats|--statistics
 ip -r
 ip -c|-color

 ip address add IFADDR dev IFNAME			# add ip address to an interface



 [objects]
 	
	link - network device
